data.description:
Wonderful Arts & Craft two story stucco 3BR 2.5BA with single attached garage. Major renovations completed in 2013 including new plumbing, shingles, kitchen, and all bathrooms. Renovations in 2015 include hardwood floors installed throughout the main floor and upstairs hallway as well as new gutters. Great location, close to schools & parks. The home also has a spacious backyard with alley access. 
Contact: haleymeis@gmail.com
